<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>名人 - 人物</title><link>https://siftrss.com/f/LbvpaQbPYJQ</link><description>来自人物的最新名人新闻、采访和故事。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 01:12:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 提出新动议，要求法官推翻马里布大厦审判中的陪审团</title><link>https://people.com/kanye-west-asks-judge-to-overturn-jury-decisions-in-malibu-mansion-trial-11928576</link><description>此前，陪审团裁定托尼·萨克森 (Tony Saxon) 赔偿 14 万美元，理由是他在韦斯特价值 5,700 万美元的加州住宅中工作时受伤。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/guTSa3p_B9CCRODY2RpfP8YKlbM=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Kanye-West-Grammys-2025-02022025-tout-1ef2107f00c34fbaa668e24d09805d36.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/kanye-west-asks-judge-to-overturn-jury-decisions-in-malibu-mansion-trial-11928576</guid></item><item><title>迄今为止我们对泰勒·弗兰基·保罗家庭暴力调查的了解</title><link>https://people.com/what-to-know-taylor-frankie-paul-domestic-violence-investigation-11928244</link><description>警方于 2026 年 2 月开始调查涉及《摩门教妻子的秘密生活》明星泰勒·弗兰基·保罗的涉嫌家庭暴力事件&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/D2cE39636fwOppcdPzUD5ICi224=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/taylor-frankie-paul-the-secret-lives-of-mormon-wives-season-2-premiere-031625-1-60b8440f9b1d48a8a3fc78664c374549.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/what-to-know-taylor-frankie-paul-domestic-violence-investigation-11928244</guid></item><item><title>泰勒·弗兰基·保罗的《单身女郎》参赛者在家庭暴力调查新闻后感到“被背叛”（独家来源）</title><link>https://people.com/taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-contestants-betrayed-source-exclusive-11927897</link><description>德雷珀市警察局证实，正在对保罗和她的前男友达科塔·莫滕森进行公开的“家庭暴力调查”，双方都提出了指控&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/NEkd5oxZvRyOEv3gVaS8VId4HD8=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-031726-e14ce0b8b77e4ea0a09811fcf7b8782f.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 20:16:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/taylor-frankie-paul-bachelorette-contestants-betrayed-source-exclusive-11927897</guid></item><item><title>泰勒·弗兰基·保罗 (Taylor Frankie Paul) 的圈子因涉嫌家庭暴力事件而“担心她的健康”（独家）</title><link>https://people.com/taylor-frankie-paul-circle-worried-for-well-being-exclusive-11928263</link><description>警方此前向《人物》杂志证实，这位《摩门教妻子的秘密生活》明星正在参与一项公开的“家庭暴力调查” &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/rQ3HhGB8d9FZkLuqvOAQyoA5rsc=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Taylor-Frankie-Paul-031726-3008af0f234e4097b8565d62ecb6c7d3.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 19:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/taylor-frankie-paul-circle-worried-for-well-being-exclusive-11928263</guid></item></channel></rss>